headline: YouTube TV Threatens a Fox Blackout Without a New Deal by Tomorrow
summary: Google's YouTube said it will shut off Fox programming, including Fox Sports, from its YouTube TV streaming service unless a new contract is reached by 5:00 p.m. ET Wednesday.
